properties.name: Cherry Blossom Shuttle Stop
properties.notes: Fee: $1 per ride. During the festival, the shuttle is an option for reaching areas of East Potomac Park, where there are more cherry trees and less crowding. The bus runs a loop from the Jefferson Memorial around Hains Point.
